{"tid":1093081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"父性侵19歲女兒判無罪　「難以認定她無力反抗」","createTime":"2019-04-05T10:39:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T07:15:15.000Z","uid":72009,"like":26,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"c3b8b16c07b0a50cb0e09525d2fc0f547c64b48c","tid":1093081,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T10:39:47.000Z","msg":"父親性侵19歲的女兒，法院認為沒辦法證明她無力反抗，判無罪 。<br />\n<br />\n據《高知新聞》報導，2017年，男子性侵當時19歲的女兒，遭檢察官指控準強制性交罪求刑10年，名古屋地方法院岡崎支部指出「無法認定被害者處於無法抵抗的狀態」，3月26日判處無罪。檢察官在審判中指出，「從國中2年級開始就持續被性虐待，因為需要家裡負擔專門學校的學費，所以在心理上無法抵抗」，不過律師反對，「雖然同意這樣的說法，但是可以抵抗」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190405/1545825/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190405%2F1545825%2F&d=K4UaoR%2Bzp7qM8XPwf0LBIw8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=761c57ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190405%2F1545825%2F&h=1b43f8e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190405/1545825/</a><br />\n<br />\n因為需要家裡負擔專門學校的學費，所以在心理上無法抵抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ae10768efa99c1790b0f921995dbb6f488f955b","tid":1093081,"uid":177089,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T10:44:43.000Z","msg":"即係誘姦合法？"},{"pid":"f7b11bbf9ba83fc2dd1ef434b6083646f56cde79","tid":1093081,"uid":94828,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T10:44:55.000Z","msg":"估錯國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"513f887f14f4196dc447fb1fcd03e243f72ae613","tid":1093081,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T10:45:48.000Z","msg":"日本亂倫合法?定係脫強姦only"},{"pid":"070bfb5026d0b2892cbcf4b27aa424893c4a1fe4","tid":1093081,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"3ae10768efa99c1790b0f921995dbb6f488f955b"